{"tid":1771102,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"美國參議員Rick Scott: 中共開始左一場新冷戰","createTime":"2019-12-05T15:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T15:33:41.000Z","uid":303462,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"02a49c18ea7cc55b7c1a593c7ba7f1263febc9a6","tid":1771102,"uid":303462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:06:55.000Z","msg":"中共以稱霸世界為目標，開始左一場新冷戰。<br />\n<br />\nCommunist China has created a new Cold War. Their goal is to dominate the world. <br />\n<br />\n但係我地始終相信民主、自由同人權對於美國強盛經濟與世界安全，至關緊要。我地會贏。<br />\n<br />\nBut we are going to win, because we believe that freedom, democracy and human rights are key to a strong American economy and a safe and secure world. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1202596335163195392?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1202596335163195392%3Fs%3D19&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScBfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=479c2c54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1202596335163195392%3Fs%3D19&h=e311ee7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1202596335163195392?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"034a2e5919dd0ad1dcbc41487183698cff0f2805","tid":1771102,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T15:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4pN6bO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4pN6bO.gif&h=f824c62d&s={SIZE}\" />  128 維園見  128 維園見  128 維園見  128 維園見 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MKG48AO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMKG48AO.jpg&h=67817e52&s={SIZE}\" />   <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SrwkGRT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSrwkGRT.jpg&h=06f56243&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dcd49bda26d1435fa21765075053c5190e1e1384","tid":1771102,"uid":70745,"like":1,"dislike